Package: blblm
Type: Package
Title: Bag of Little Bootstraps for Linear Regression Model
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Xiaoqi", "Na", email = "xna@ucdavis.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: blblm is to compute the bag of little bootstraps for linear regression model.
    blblm can return the coefficient, sigma, confident interval and prodiction of the bootstraps for linear regression model, and also it can print out the model.
